NEW ORLEANS COAL & BISSO TOWBOAT COMPANY, By and Through Its Receiver, Joseph A. Bisso, et al., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America et al., Appellee. No. 8055. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Dec. 12, 1936. For original opinion, see 86 F.(2d) 53.

Before FOSTER, HUTCHESON, and HOLMES, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

As neither of the judges who concurred in the judgment of the court in the above numbered and entitled cause is of opinion that the petitions for rehearing should be granted, it is ordered that the said petitions be, and the same hereby are,

Denied.
